	Tagged as v1.0

	* retroarch.cfg: Initial drop-in configuration
	  - Target: Apple TV 4K 3rd Gen (2022), A15 Bionic, 128 GB
	  - Software: RetroArch v1.22.x (App Store), tvOS 18+
	  - 25 active keys across 9 sections (menu, video, audio, latency,
	    hotkeys, directories, cloud sync, save management, rewind)
	  - 6 reference sections (CRT shaders, BIOS, cores, folders, checklist,
	    known issues, 4th Gen projections)
